dialogue0.0: According to all known laws of aviation, there is no way a bee should be able to fly.

dialogue0.1: Its wings are too small to get its fat little body off the ground.

dialogue0.2: The bee, of course, flies anyway because bees don't care what humans think is impossible.

dialogue1.0: Some...body once told me the world is gonna roll me

dialogue1.1: I ain't the sharpest tool in the shed

dialogue1.2: She was looking kinda dumb with her finger and her thumb in the shape of an 'L' on her forehead
